Enjoy safe, secure and smart living with the Germanica Smart Home app. Control your Germanica Smart Home products remotely through Wi-Fi. Set automations and schedules to what best suits your home!
After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our “Germanica Smart Home” app in app market then register an account;
(2). Configure our devices in our “Germanica Smart Home” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4). Search “Germanica Smart Home” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5). Enable “Germanica Smart Home” skill, and you'll be navigated to “Germanica Smart Home” login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, turn on the kettle
Alexa, turn on the fan
Alexa, set the fan to 1
Alexa, turn off the heater
Alexa, start the robot
Alexa, set the robot to dock
